:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"以下收集實用tg channel link<br />\n叫雞谷走開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/weatherjj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJufjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=3c608398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/weatherjj</a><br />\n<blockquote>本頻道主要提供：<br />\n✅天氣實況及短中期預報；<br />\n✅大型公眾活動現場實況及民防資訊；<br />\n✅本地、國際新聞分享及簡評；<br />\n✅其他與個人防護相關的資訊（例：法律知識、衛生資訊）。<br />\n<br />\n注意本頻道：<br />\n‼️提供非官方天氣資訊，如希望獲取官方資訊，請參閱香港天文台網頁；<br />\n‼️僅提供大型公眾活動的民防資訊，不會提倡現場民眾作任何行動；<br />\n‼️提供的新聞簡評、法律意見、衛生提示及交通消息等僅為個人意見，參考前請自行判斷。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ebfd0477635e51e088b069d76744ac0c9a68d514","tid":2363270,"uid":4250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:00:17.000Z","msg":"呢個真係要推<br />\n好多人唔用tg話因為加太多Channel 同group好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69eb10b331a442064c6377fc182b2af88b01daf9","tid":2363270,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"你直接撳Personal 咪得囉😛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860cfdb9d0698a6aab16081a45b3c954b80afa66","tid":2363270,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69eb10b331a442064c6377fc182b2af88b01daf9","tid":2363270,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"你直接撳Personal 咪得囉😛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:01:48.000Z","msg":"mm get"},{"pid":"59f336a9f9e2d6d28157b31c2837ca02408b167b","tid":2363270,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69eb10b331a442064c6377fc182b2af88b01daf9","tid":2363270,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"你直接撳Personal 咪得囉😛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=